                     <interp inst="t17850406-57-off278" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17850406-57-cd279" type="crimeDate">20th day of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850406-57-off278 t17850406-57-cd279"></join> last, one cushion made of woollen cloth and canvas stuffed with feathers, value 9 s.
            </rs> the proproperty of 
               
                  <persName id="t17850406-57-victim632" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Hughes
                  <interp inst="t17850406-57-victim632" type="surname" value="Hughes"></interp>
